<HEADLINE> Kiefer Sutherland Files for Divorce  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
   LOS ANGELES (AP) -- Kiefer Sutherland filed for divorce from
Kelly Winn Sutherland, his wife of three years, citing
irreconcilable differences.
</P>
<P>
   The 33-year-old star of ''Young Guns,'' ''Flatliners'' and ''The
Lost Boys'' had been formally separated from his wife since June
30, according to the petition filed this week in Superior Court.
</P>
<P>
   The two married Sept. 1, 1996, the same year the actor worked
with his father, Donald Sutherland, in ''A Time to Kill.''
</P>
