   Sears and AOL are teaming up in a wide-ranging alliance through
which they will develop Internet-linked appliances for the home and
will market each other's services. The companies plan to develop a
special co-branded edition of AOL, which will offer special Sears
promotions and links to Sears' Web sites.
</P>
<P>
Cordant Technologies Inc., up 25{ at 55 1/16
Alcoa Inc., down 6 13/16 at 61\
</P>
<P>
