the mound as he sprinted in from the right-field bullpen in the ninth inning of
the Atlanta Braves' game against Detroit tonight. In his first action since the
World Series -- and his controversial magazine interview -- Rocker pitched a
1-2-3 ninth inning in the Braves' 4-0 win.
</P>
